  "general_provisions": "This bill directs the Gary R. Herbert Institute for Public Policy at Utah Valley University and the Center for Constitutional Studies at Utah Valley University to conduct an elections study.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet> directs the Gary R. Herbert Institute for Public Policy at Utah Valley University  (the institute) and the Center for Constitutional Studies at Utah Valley University (the center) to conduct an elections study regarding:<hr><ltbullet1>the security of in-person voting versus voting by mail; and<hr><ltbullet1>best practices for conducting and implementing a process where identification must be presented before depositing a ballot in a ballot drop box; and<hr><ltbullet>directs the institute and the center to present the study to the Government Operations Interim Committee. ",
  "monies": "None",
  "attorney": "Thomas R. Vaughn",
